        "created_at": "2023-11-01T18:55:10.490Z",
        "cooked": "<p>How did it/the UI work? Would it still send them as one message, but allowed individual captions? Or if you specified some individual captions, would it then break those images out into separate messages?</p>\n<p>And do you recall how the UI worked/looked to be able to specify individual captions?</p>\n<p>I don‚Äôt remember this feature (I was definitely using Signal then), but it sounds intriguing and very useful!</p>",
